OL,3,CSecret Garden Cafe owner wins fight to
OL,4,Cstay in Bute Park
OL,6,FThe woman who runs a popular park cafe
OL,7,Fwill continue to run it for a further
OL,8,Ffive years after her future at the
OL,9,Fpremises seemed in doubt.
OL,11,Fstarted lease negotiations with the
OL,12,Foperator of The Secret Garden Cafe at
OL,13,FBute Park, Melissa Boothman, in 2022
OL,14,Fand informed her the following year
OL,15,Fthat her offers for a renewal would
OL,16,Fnot be accepted.
