OL,6,FThe local authority put a new
OL,7,Fmanagement agreement and associated
OL,8,Flease out to market through Sell 2
OL,9,FWales in December before announcing in
OL,10,FMarch that it had found an operator to
OL,11,Faward it to.
OL,13,FThe local authority said at the time
OL,14,Fthat it could not reveal the identity
OL,15,Fof the proposed new operator during a
OL,16,Ftwo-week legalling process and call-in
OL,17,Fwindow which came to a close on
OL,18,FMonday, April 8.
