OL,6,FA Cardiff Council spokesperson said:
OL,7,F"We are delighted to report that `
OL,8,Ffollowing a full and proper
OL,9,Fprocurement process ` the council has
OL,10,Fawarded a five-year concession
OL,11,Fagreement and associated lease to the
OL,12,Fcurrent operator of the Secret Garden
OL,13,FCafe in Bute Park.
