OL,6,F"We look forward to continuing our
OL,7,Fworking relationship with the
OL,8,Fleaseholder and we know the cafe will
OL,9,Fcontinue to play its part in helping
OL,10,Fus meet the needs of the hundreds of
OL,11,Fthousands of people who visit the
OL,12,Faward-winning green heart of the city
OL,13,Fevery year."
OL,15,FVisitors to Bute Park and The Secret
OL,16,FGarden Cafe came out in their
OL,17,Fthousands to show their support for Ms
OL,18,FBoothman and her team when it was
OL,19,Freported that she could be leaving the
OL,20,Fpremises.
