OL,6,FPeople also noted the contribution the
OL,7,Fcafe under Ms Boothman has made to the
OL,8,Fpark and community over the years,
OL,9,Fincluding the thousands of pounds it
OL,10,Fput towards repairing the park and
OL,11,Freplanting trees and the thousands of
OL,12,Fpounds donated to various charities.
OL,14,FThe Secret Garden Cafe was previously
OL,15,Fheld under a property lease.
