OL,3,CSecret Garden Cafe owner wins fight to
OL,4,Cstay in Bute Park
OL,6,FAt the beginning of 2023, the council
OL,7,Fsought legal advice on offers put
OL,8,Fforward by Ms Boothman and decided a
OL,9,Fmanagement agreement instead of a
OL,10,Fproperty lease agreement was the best
OL,11,Fway forward for the premises.
OL,13,FCardiff Council's decision to go out
OL,14,Fto tender was called in for scrutiny
OL,15,Fby Liberal Democrats councillor, Cllr
OL,16,FRhys Taylor, in August 2023 to look at
OL,17,Fwhether the process followed by the
OL,18,Flocal authority had been fair to the
OL,19,Ftenant.
