OL,6,FThe council's head of economic
OL,7,Fdevelopment, Neil Hanratty, said at
OL,8,Fthe meeting that he regretted the
OL,9,Fanxiety the process of deciding the
OL,10,Ffuture of the cafe caused Ms Boothman
OL,11,Fand her staff.
OL,13,FHe also encouraged Ms Boothman to bid
OL,14,Fwhen the management agreement went out
OL,15,Fto market and apologised for the
OL,16,Fperiod of time it took for the council
OL,17,Fto get to a point where it understood
OL,18,Fthat a concession agreement was needed.
